# 🌐 The Complete Deployment Guide — From Zero to Production
## For Full-Stack ML Applications (Frontend + FastAPI + ML Models + Database + External Services)

> **Purpose:** A universal, reusable, extremely detailed guide for deploying any project that has a **React/Vite frontend**, a **Python/FastAPI backend with ML models**, a **managed database**, and **external services** (IPFS, cloud storage, APIs, etc.)
>
> **Use this for ANY project** — not tied to a specific codebase.

